All the percentages for electoral demographics are calculated by Tindak Malaysia using Electoral Roll data. There is no official ethnic demographic data. All ethnic data is an estimate. There could be slight overcounting of Bidayuh voters and slight undercounting of Iban voters. TindakMalaysia Network Services PLT is not responsible for any errors or ommissions arising from the original data or its derivatives
